{"tid":667241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國又輸] 歐盟擬用歐元代替美元結算與伊朗石油貿易","createTime":"2018-05-16T14:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T05:14:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c93dc55ffbea63b892cc1e65b2328a1ee8757a","tid":667241,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"歐盟擬用歐元代替美元結算與伊朗石油貿易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180516/bkn-20180516184740254-0516_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180516%2Fbkn-20180516184740254-0516_00842_001.html&d=UqDTeOLwe1JSaJPeU29b7%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e72bf83a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180516/bkn-20180516184740254-0516_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟計劃與伊朗石油貿易時，採用歐元代替美元進行結算。<br />\n<br />\n美國單方面退出伊朗核協議後，歐盟和伊朗會保持並深化經濟合作，包括在石油和天然氣方面的合作。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟外交事務代表莫格里尼表示，在與來自英國、法國、德國和伊朗四國外長商談後，各國達成一致，在接下來幾個星期裡，商談更具體的解決方案應對美國退出伊核協議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9f8414e8cabaa9719b30cf991c7ec52c4f6cfd","tid":667241,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"Europe to ditch US dollar in payments for Iranian oil &ndash; source<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rt.com/business/426856-europe-to-ditch-us-dollar/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rt.com%2Fbusiness%2F426856-europe-to-ditch-us-dollar%2F&d=UqDTeOLwe1JSaJPeU29b7%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=68cb5244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rt.com/business/426856-europe-to-ditch-us-dollar/</a><br />\n<br />\nThe European Union is planning to switch payments to the euro for its oil purchases from Iran, eliminating US dollar transactions, a diplomatic source told RIA Novosti.<br />\n<br />\nBrussels has been at odds with Washington over the US withdrawal from the Iran nuclear deal, which was reached during the administration of Barack Obama. President Donald Trump has pledged to re-impose sanctions against the Islamic Republic.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;m privy to the information that the EU is going to shift from dollar to euro to pay for crude from Iran,&rdquo; the source told the agency.</span><br />\n<br />\nEarlier this week, EU foreign policy chief Federica Mogherini said that the foreign ministers of the UK, France, Germany, and Iran had agreed to work out practical solutions in response to Washington&rsquo;s move in the next few weeks. The bloc is reportedly planning to maintain and deepen economic ties with Iran, including in the area of oil and gas supplies.<br />\n<br />\nMogherini stressed that the sides should jointly work on the lifting of sanctions as an integral part of the historic nuclear deal. &ldquo;We're not naive and know it will be difficult for all sides.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe Iran nuclear deal, known as the Joint Comprehensive Plan of Action (JCPOA), was sealed three years ago in Vienna between Tehran and the P5+1 powers (China, France, Russia, UK, US, plus Germany). The agreement saw decades-long international sanctions lifted in exchange for Iran curbing its controversial nuclear program. On January 16, 2016, the parties to the deal announced the beginning of its implementation.<br />\n<br />\nThe lifting of international sanctions gave Iran access to the world&rsquo;s markets for the first time in nearly four decades. Since then, Tehran has managed to significantly increase its exports of crude.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25152d5a8e0eebf130da5c2c67348caeaf7d1e16","tid":667241,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"暫時淨係見到RT之類ge source <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔見大路歐美新聞機構報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73086066daf4b45f7f3d71fc8386f71a1ab49fe8","tid":667241,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"嘩，堅唔堅呀，咁大膽"},{"pid":"0c1d211a494edfbeed3364c18908e8bf0eb13f23","tid":667241,"uid":76216,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"如果係真<br />\n咁等解體啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23b893ce84cbbba7c19ca42f47aa2a1731520ce","tid":667241,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c1d211a494edfbeed3364c18908e8bf0eb13f23","tid":667241,"uid":76216,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"如果係真<br />\n咁等解體啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"美帝出手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbacf3cefa6dfe986d3c5ce744d34cbc221982f1","tid":667241,"uid":25424,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"25152d5a8e0eebf130da5c2c67348caeaf7d1e16","tid":667241,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"暫時淨係見到RT之類ge source <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔見大路歐美新聞機構報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"如果真，美國即刻退出北約，睇下邊個驚D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa21313a1a472c02804015aaf17ed94ce912177","tid":667241,"uid":8439,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"唔用美金找數 睇下美帝打唔打柒你"},{"pid":"